<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/730849-i-ve-never-been-able-to-understand-the">I&#39;ve never been able to understand the history of this book. It was originally published in 1989? And then she rewrote parts of it when it was rereleased in 2000? Or was it only published in 2000?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_730849'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F331010.Sunglasses_After_Dark">like</a></span>

