<span id="freeTextContainer7517658966105146038">Interesting world this is set in but it does have some issues.<br/><br/>It was a bit of a mess of flashbacks, bit part characters and side character introductions. When the bad (or lack of) editing wasn&apos;t present there was some ok scenes but the whole origin story etc shoved any actual plot out of the way so when you got back to it you just didn&apos;t really care or had forgotten who was who and what they had to do with anything.<br/><br/>The editing issues apparently stem from the author &apos;modernising&apos; the story to inc</span>
