    <a title="chucklesthescot" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/3426724-chucklesthescot"><img alt="chucklesthescot" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1537360628p2/3426724.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/121584461?book_show_action=true">Sep 14, 2010</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="chucklesthescot" class="user" itemprop="url" name="chucklesthescot" href="/user/show/3426724-chucklesthescot">chucklesthescot</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="did not like it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">did not like it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title=" 9780708844793" href="/book/show/2569092-sunglasses-after-dark">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3426724-chucklesthescot?shelf=fiction">fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3426724-chucklesthescot?shelf=abandoned">abandoned</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3426724-chucklesthescot?shelf=uf-pnr">uf-pnr</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3426724-chucklesthescot?shelf=vampires">vampires</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer121584461" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7027850342996627944">Sonja Blue is locked up in an institution for the insane and is feared by staff and inmates alike as her monstrous side can enter their dreams to bring them terror and pain. So when she escapes a lot of people need to start worrying.<br/><br/>I found the whole alter ego thing to be very confusing. You seem to be getting told that Sonja is the evil part of the partnership but you can never tell exactly which personality is in control at what time. When inside Sonja&apos;s head you&apos;re not sure which part of her </span>
  <span id="freeText7027850342996627944" style="display:none">Sonja Blue is locked up in an institution for the insane and is feared by staff and inmates alike as her monstrous side can enter their dreams to bring them terror and pain. So when she escapes a lot of people need to start worrying.<br /><br />I found the whole alter ego thing to be very confusing. You seem to be getting told that Sonja is the evil part of the partnership but you can never tell exactly which personality is in control at what time. When inside Sonja's head you're not sure which part of her is actually thinking. Confusing and frustrating and not very well written.</span>
